text: "Stressed Out" is a 1996 song by A Tribe Called Quest featuring Faith Evans. It is the second single from their fourth studio album Beats, Rhymes and Life and went to number 33 in the United Kingdom, number 81 in Scotland and number 15 on the Billboard Hot Rap Songs chart. ==Track listing== ===12" single=== A-side #"Stressed Out" (Baby Phife Version - Full) #"Stressed Out" (Raphael Saadiq's Remix) #"Stressed Out" (LP Version) B-side #"1nce Again" (LP Version) #"1nce Again" (Jay Dee's Instrumental) #"Stressed Out" (Baby Phife Instrumental) ==References== Category:1996 songs Category:A Tribe Called Quest songs Category:Faith Evans songs Category:Hip hop songs
title: Stressed Out (A Tribe Called Quest song)
